{
  "stem": "24651.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember certain dishes that to this day, I kind of favor, you know, like sliced cumbers called mizeria with cream and [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] borscht.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, I mean, different things, but not always the same things.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, we lived in a-- I think it was an apartment.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't remember exactly where we lived, but I-- it wasn't a house.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I remember a couple incidents that happened.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Once-- well, I must have been two, three years old.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was a beautiful table cloth on the table, in the dining room table.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My mother did a craft called tatting.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was kind of an embroidery, but lace-- sort of lace making.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I remember having a wonderful time cutting it up with scissors.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And another time, I remember the housekeeper was cleaning out the bird cage.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the bird was on the balcony.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she told me to hold the door closed, you know, not to let him out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Of course, I did let him out and the neighbors running around looking for a canary that was flying around.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Different little things-- I remember the first time my parents went out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I was still in a crib.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The crib was made out of like, a netting, like a rope, rope netting.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And my parents were going out for the evening and leaving me with the housekeeper.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I remember you know, carrying on, screaming.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And that was my first experience with separation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And it's so incredible, because I remember the design of the nightgown that I was wearing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I must have been really little, because I was still in a crib.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So things like that, you know, those very early memories-- but mainly the family and the warmth of the family.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
